Travelling along embombutmaronsambalat road in the&nbsp;Kerio valley triangle, a motorist is treated to a rare&nbsp;adventure and sensation of the great Elgeyo escarpment.&nbsp;Nonetheless, with its rock-filled hills and numerous sharp&nbsp;meanders, motorists undergo a spine-chilling experience&nbsp;that only a few can attempt. Despite the adventure of the&nbsp;area, the road is fast proving to be a death trap.
